    • Constructor Detail

      • ArCamera

        public ArCamera(float fov,
                float aspectRatio,
                float roll,
                float pitch,
                float yaw,
                float height)
        Deprecated. 

        Virtual AR camera parameters.

        Parameters:
        fov - Vertical field of view expressed in radians
        aspectRatio - Aspect ratio
        roll - Roll of the camera in radians.Expresses rotation around Y axis (goes from the right to the left of the vehicle).Device pointing straight to the road will have roll = pi/2 radians (90 degrees).
        pitch - Pitch of the camera in radians.Expresses rotation around Z axis (goes from the bottom to the top of the vehicle).Device pointing straight to the road will have pitch = 0 radians.
        yaw - Yaw of the camera in radians.Expresses rotation around X axis (goes from the end to the front of the vehicle).Device pointing straight to the road will have yaw = 0 radians.
        height - Height above the road surface in meters
